stitem [ref=e662]: Support the Windows 11 Moment 2 taskbar\n                      - listitem [ref=e663]: Fix newly created windows thinking they where the active window when this wasn't the case\n                      - listitem [ref=e664]: Fix hide tray being hit twice not showing the dialog anymore\n                    - heading \"Various improvements/changes\" [level=1] [ref=e665]\n                    - list [ref=e666]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e667]:\n                        - text: \"New supported languages:\"\n                        - list [ref=e668]:\n                          - listitem [ref=e669]: German\n                          - listitem [ref=e670]: Spanish (United States)\n                          - listitem [ref=e671]: Turkish\n                          - listitem [ref=e672]: Indonesian\n                          - listitem [ref=e673]: Russian (Russia)\n                      - listitem [ref=e674]: Improved Simplified Chinese translation\n                      - listitem [ref=e675]: Localize more user-facing strings\n                      - listitem [ref=e676]: Add hidden configuration options to override the language used by TranslucentTB\n                      - listitem [ref=e677]: Add hidden configuration options to disable the new XAML context menu\n                      - listitem [ref=e678]: Update WinUI to 2.8.4\n                      - listitem [ref=e679]: Add a tooltip when the titlebar text overflows in windows\n                    - separator [ref=e680]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e681]:\n                      - text: As always, you can download this release from the\n                      - link \"Microsoft Store\" [ref=e682] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9PF4KZ2VN4W9\n                      - text: \", or by\"\n                      - link \"downloading and opening the TranslucentTB.appinstaller file below\" [ref=e683] [cursor=pointer]:\n                   