       - generic [ref=e128]:\n                    - heading \"Bug fixes\" [level=1] [ref=e129]\n                    - list [ref=e130]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e131]: Use a thread for initial XAML diagnostics initialization, to hopefully solve time out issues\n                      - listitem [ref=e132]: Make MultitaskingViewVisibilitySink agile to hopefully reduce issues with desktop switching and Win-Tab\n                      - listitem [ref=e133]: Add functionality to allow killing Explorer when the package gets uninstalled, which should solve issues when the app is immediately reinstalled after being uninstalled\n                      - listitem [ref=e134]: Fix compatibility issues with application that fake a taskbar\n                    - heading \"Various improvements/changes\" [level=1] [ref=e135]\n                    - list [ref=e136]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e137]: Support taskbar preview via window messages\n                    - separator [ref=e138]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e139]:\n                      - text: As always, you can download this release from the\n                      - link \"Microsoft Store\" [ref=e140] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9PF4KZ2VN4W9\n                      - text: \", or by\"\n                      - link \"downloading and opening the TranslucentTB.appinstaller file below\" [ref=e141] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/download/2026.1/TranslucentTB.appinstaller\n                        - text: downloading and opening the\n                        - code [ref=e142]: TranslucentTB.appinstaller\n                        - text: file below\n                      - text: . Additionally, Windows 11 users can download the portable version by\n                      - link \"downloading TranslucentTB-portable-x64.zip\" [ref=e143] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  