6]:\n                    - generic [ref=e467]: Compare\n                    - generic:\n                      - img\n              - generic [ref=e469]:\n                - generic [ref=e470]:\n                  - link \"2024.1\" [ref=e475] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: /TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/tag/2024.1\n                  - generic [ref=e476]:\n                    - paragraph [ref=e477]: This release is signed with Azure Code Signing! Future releases will be using ACS as well. ACS creates short-lived certificates for signature so the thumbprint is not fixed, however the certificate subject will always be the same.\n                    - heading \"Bug fixes\" [level=1] [ref=e478]\n                    - list [ref=e479]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e480]: Fix portable builds not working if the TranslucentTB temporary directory didn't exist.\n                      - listitem [ref=e481]: Fix erroneous \"Couldn't configure TAP to restore taskbar appearance once TranslucentTB dies.\" message in the log.\n                      - listitem [ref=e482]: Make Start opened, Search opened and Task View opened states work on newer builds of Windows 11.\n                      - listitem [ref=e483]: Fix crashes with GlazeWM and the Magnifier app.\n                      - listitem [ref=e484]: Increase the timeout for the XAML TAP to hopefully reduce the amount of \"The wait operation timed out\" and \"Element not found\" messages being seen.\n                    - heading \"Various improvements/changes\" [level=1] [ref=e485]\n                    - list [ref=e486]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e487]: Support for Ukrainian locale.\n                      - listitem [ref=e488]: Improvements to German and Chinese translations.\n                      - listitem [ref=e489]: This releases uses a new GUID for the tray icon, because the ACS certificate subject is different than the previous certificate. Due to this, your preferences related to the tray icon will be reset.\n                      - listitem [ref=e490]:\n                        - text: Remove the\n                        - code [ref=e491]: \"ttb:\"\n                        - text: protocol, as it was an experiment for something that didn't end up working.\n                    - separator [ref=e492]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e493]:\n                      - text: As always, you can download this release from the\n                      - link \"Microsoft Store\" [ref=e494] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9PF4KZ2VN4W9\n                      - text: \", or by\"\n                      - link \"downloading and opening the TranslucentTB.appinstaller file below\" [ref=e495] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/download/2024.1/TranslucentTB.appinstaller\n                        - text: downloading and opening the\n                        - code [ref=e496]: TranslucentTB.appinstaller\n                        - text: file below\n                      - text: . Additionally, Windows 11 users can download the portable version by\n                      - link \"downloading TranslucentTB-portable-x64.zip\" [ref=e497] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://github.com/TranslucentTB/TranslucentTB/releases/download/2024.1/TranslucentTB-portable-x64.zip\n                        - text: downloading\n                        - code [ref=e498]: TranslucentTB-portable-x64.zip\n                      - text: .\n                - generic [ref=e499]:\n                  - group [ref=e502]:\n                    - button \"Assets 10\" [ref=e503] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - generic [ref=e504]:\n                        - generic [ref=e505]: Assets\n                        - generic \"10\" [ref=e506]\n                  - generic [ref=e508]:\n                    - generic [ref=e510]:\n                      