{"type":"message","id":"aa9a4c42","parentId":"1e36a21f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T08:09:52.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户希望我把更新壁纸的操作整理成一个可靠的工作流，这样以后就不会再出错了。我需要创建一个自动化脚本来处理壁纸更换的所有步骤。\n\n让我创建一个完整的工作流脚本，包含：\n1. 下载壁纸的备用方案\n2. 正确的注册表设置\n3. 强制刷新桌面\n\n我会把这个工作流写成文档或脚本，保存在用户的电脑上。","thinkingSignature":"8345e7a4261d3a171f6c4c503deb33977770d484797316a10ba2626065ca1a80"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hc2a1mfxbzdx_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 壁纸更换工作流\n\n> 作者：AI 助手\n> 日期：2026-03-17\n> 用途：可靠更换 Windows 桌面壁纸\n\n---\n\n## 工作流脚本\n\n将以下代码保存为 `C:\\Users\\16343\\Downloads\\set-wallpaper.ps1`\n\n```powershell\n# ============================================\n# Windows 壁纸更换工作流\n# ============================================\n\nparam(\n    [Parameter(Mandatory=$false)]\n    [string]$ImagePath = \"C:\\Users\\16343\\Downloads\\wallpaper.jpg\"\n)\n\n# 检查图片是否存在\nif (-not (Test-Path $ImagePath)) {\n    Write-Host \"[错误] 图片不存在: $ImagePath\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\n# 获取图片大小\n$fileSize = (Get-Item $ImagePath).Length\nWrite-Host \"[信息] 图片大小: $([math]::Round($fileSize/1MB, 2)) MB\"\n\nif ($fileSize -lt 100000) {\n    Write-Host \"[警告] 图片太小，可能是缩略图\"\n}\n\n# ============================================\n# 步骤 1: 设置注册表\n# ============================================\nWrite-Host \"[步骤 1] 设置注册表...\"\n\nSet-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop' -Name Wallpaper -Value $ImagePath -Type String\nSet-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop' -Name WallpaperStyle -Value 0 -Type String\nSet-ItemProperty -Path 'HKCU:\\Control Panel\\Desktop' -Name TileWallpaper -Value 0 -Type String\n\n# ============================================\n# 步骤 2: 调用 SystemParametersInfo API\n# ============================================\nWrite-Host \"[步骤 2] 调用系统 API...\"\n\nAdd-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\npublic class WallpaperSetter {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\", CharSet = CharSet.Auto, SetLastError = true)]\n    public static extern int SystemParametersInfo(int uAction, int uParam, string lpvParam, int fuWinIni);\n}\n\"@\n\n$SPI_SETDESKWALLPAPER = 0x0014\n$SPIF_UPDATEINIFILE = 0x01\n$SPIF_SENDCHANGE = 0x02\n\n$result = [WallpaperSetter]::SystemParametersInfo(\n    $SPI_SETDESKWALLPAPER, \n    0, \n    $ImagePath, \n    $SPIF_UPDATEINIFILE -bor $SPIF_SENDCHANGE\n)\n\nif ($result -eq 0) {\n    Write-Host \"[错误] API 调用失败\"\n    exit 1\n}\n\nWrite-Host \"[成功] API 调用返回: $result\"\n\n# ============================================\n#步骤 3: 重启 Explorer\n# ============================================\nWrite-Host \"[步骤 3] 重启资源管理器...\"\n\nStop-Process -Name explorer -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nStart-Process explorer\n\nWrite-Host \"[完成] 壁纸更换完成！\"\nWrite-Host \"图片路径: $ImagePath\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## 备选壁纸位置\n\n如果网络下载失败，使用以下本地高质量壁纸：\n\n| 路径 | 大小 | 描述 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `C:\\Windows\\Web\\Wallpaper\\Windows\\img0.jpg` | 1.6MB | Windows 默认壁纸 |\n| `C:\\Windows\\Web\\Wallpaper\\Windows\\img19.jpg` | 1.3MB | Windows 4K 壁纸 |\n| `C:\\Windows\\Web\\4K\\Wallpaper\\Windows\\img0_1920x1200.jpg` | 542KB | 4K 壁纸 |\n\n---\n\n## 使用方法\n\n1. **更换壁纸**：\n   ```powershell\n   powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\\Users\\16343\\Downloads\\set-wallpaper.ps1\n   ```\n\n2. **更换为本地图片**：\n   ```powershell\n   powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\\Users\\16343\\Downloads\\set-wallpaper.ps1 -ImagePath \"你的图片路径.jpg\"\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## 故障排查\n\n| 问题 | 解决方案 |\n|------|---------|\n| 壁纸是黑的 | 检查图片大小是否 >100KB，确保不是缩略图 |\n| 壁纸不变 | 确保 WallpaperStyle=0, TileWallpaper=0 |\n| 还是不变 | 重启 Explorer 或注销账户 |\n\n---\n\n## 注意事项\n\n1. **绝不使用用户的截图/隐私图片**\n2. **优先使用本地系统壁纸**\n3. **图片大小至少 500KB 以上**\n4. **执行后检查注册表确认**\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\Downloads\\壁纸工作流.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":60,"output":1084,"cacheRead":25364,"cacheWrite":116963,"totalTokens":143471,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite